Update your dynamic zones directly from Perl. This module is a simple
wrapper around the nsupdate program, distributed as part of Bind9. You
start by adding some instructions to the module, and then run execute.

INSTALLATION

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

AVAILABILITY

  Latest stable version is available on CPAN. Current development
  version is available on https://github.com/olof/Net-Bind9-Update.

VERSION NUMBERING

  The version numbers should be read as a floating point value,
  where 0.9 is higher than 0.89.
